"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabaAtN waAfirN","text_ar":"نَبَاتٌ وَافِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Full,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complete,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant, property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N mawofuwrN","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ مَوْفُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is full, complete,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazaA='N muwaf~arN","text_ar":"جَزَا=ءٌ مُوَفَّرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A recompense of which nothing is deficient."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aEari","text_ar":"الشَّعَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN muwaf~aru","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ مُوَفَّرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has his hair left to become abundant and long."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqaA='N","text_ar":"سِقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awofaru","text_ar":"اَوْفَرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waforN","text_ar":"وَفْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A skin for milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water, made of hide of which nothing is deficient."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, A, K.) And in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdapN waforaA='u","text_ar":"مَزَادَةٌ وَفْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A leather water-bag made of a complete skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nothing thereof being deficient:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) also signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a leather water-bag filled"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, * TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"completely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN waforaA='u","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ وَفْرَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land in the herbage of which is abundance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, * TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land of which the herbage has not been diminished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^u*unN waforaA='u","text_ar":"اُذُنٌ وَفْرَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ear having a large lobe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a large ear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large in the lobe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo mutawaAfiruwna","text_ar":"هُمْ مُتَوَافِرُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are numerous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwaAfiru","text_ar":"الوَافِرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fourth metre"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHor","text_ar":"بَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in prosody;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the measure of which consists of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEalatuno","text_ar":"مُفَاعَلَتُنْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"six times"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in its original state]: (Sgh, K:) or, [in practice,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEalatuno mufaAEalatuno faEuwluno","text_ar":"مُفَاعَلَتُنْ مُفَاعَلَتُنْ فَعُولُنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEalatuno","text_ar":"مُفَاعَلَتُنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufaAEalatuno","text_ar":"مُفَاعَلَتُنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L:) so called because its feet are made full like those of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAmil","text_ar":"كَامِل"},{"kind":"text","text":", except that there is [in practice] an elision in their letters, so that it is not complete. (M, L.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","A","K","Sgh","TA","M","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}